  "title": "Clinic Executive - Entry Level",
  "description": "<h3><strong>About the Role</strong></h3>\n<p>Our client is looking for a motivated and responsible individual to join their team as a <strong>Clinic Executive</strong>. This role is suitable for those starting their careers and keen to develop their skills in clinic operations and customer service. Comprehensive training will be provided.</p>\n<h3><br></h3>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Welcome and assist patients in a courteous and professional manner</li>\n  <li>Handle patient registration, appointment scheduling, and follow-ups</li>\n  <li>Perform basic administrative tasks and ensure records are accurately maintained</li>\n  <li>Support doctors and clinical staff in daily clinic operations</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and orderliness of the clinic environment</li>\n  <li>Learn and apply clinic systems, protocols, and standard operating procedures</li>\n  <li>Respond to general enquiries and provide quality customer service</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><br></h3>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>Diploma in any discipline</strong></li>\n  <li>No prior experience required – <strong>training will be provided</strong></li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Responsible, punctual, and able to work independently and as part of a team</li>\n  <li>Strong willingness to learn and contribute to the team</li>\n  <li>Ability to multitask in a dynamic environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
